---
title: "withdrawNonAllowlistedAssets (FeeAggregator)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: check assetAmounts.length
    q_check_empty --> q_error_empty: length == 0
    q_error_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_loop: length > 0
    q_loop --> q_check_allowlisted: for each assetAmount
    q_check_allowlisted --> q_error_allowed: s_allowlistedAssets.contains(asset)
    q_error_allowed --> [*]: revert AssetAllowlisted
    q_check_allowlisted --> q_transfer: !allowlisted
    q_transfer --> q_loop: _transferAsset(to, asset, amount)
    q_loop --> [*]: all assets withdrawn

    note right of q_check_allowlisted
        INV-001: Only non-allowlisted assets can be withdrawn through this function
        INV-002: Prevents accidental withdrawal of protocol-managed assets
        INV-003: Caller must have WITHDRAWER_ROLE
    end note
